---
title: Herb Butter-Grilled Steak with Potato Salad plus Lemony Greens & Grape Tomatoes
description: The father in your life will love this dee-luxe four-course steak ’n’ potatoes dinner. It’s a sweet way to show you care—via the tummy! There’s a creamy, mustardy potato salad, lemony greens and grape tomatoes sprinkled with Parmesan cheese, and the main event: a juicy grilled bavette steak with a rich dollop of herb butter.
